1
00:00:01,530 --> 00:00:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it Your Grace who sent 
Scarlett to the scaffold?</font>

2
00:00:06,320 --> 00:00:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What makes you think so?</font>

3
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The conclusive evidence
 in Cecilia's attempted assassination</font>

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was the bottle of poison 
found in Scarlett's chambers.</font>

5
00:00:17,450 --> 00:00:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone snuck through a duke's house
 and planted that in his daughter's room.</font>

6
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:25,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only one person could do that 
without leaving a trace,</font>

7
00:00:27,220 --> 00:00:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that person is you.</font>

8
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You arranged Scarlett's execution.</font>

9
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Strangely, he and I came
 into the world on the same day.</i></font>

10
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'm so capable that 
I surprise even myself,</font>

11
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I still wish to serve you.</font>

12
00:02:18,770 --> 00:02:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So take pride, Ern.</font>

13
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dolphy, you can't be serious.</font>

14
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remarry? Me?</font>

15
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Republic of Soldita is begging me</font>

16
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to take a descendant 
of Cornelia Faris off their hands.</font>

17
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't trust a lineage that dangerous 
to just any noble house.</font>

18
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:46,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, well, you're my only real option.</font>

19
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly... The things I do for you.</font>

20
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:58,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Aliénore Shibola.</font>

21
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My bride from across the sea 
was the very picture of a good wife.</i></font>

22
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her singular shortcoming
 was her frail constitution.</i></font>

23
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, it wasn't long
 before we had Scarlett.</i></font>

24
00:03:18,990 --> 00:03:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't help it.</font>

25
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was out of my hands, I tell you!</font>

26
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coochie coochie coo.</font>

27
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beauty you are!</font>

28
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you don't cry at the sight of me!</font>

29
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dylan, don't hold her too long. 
What if your stupidity rubs off on her?</font>

30
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

31
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you hear that, sire?! 
Wasn't that uncalled for?!</font>

32
00:03:41,070 --> 00:03:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I heard it, and I share his concern.</font>

33
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better hand 
dear little Scarlett back to me.</font>

34
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do I do? I'm surrounded by enemies!</font>

35
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looking back, those might 
have been the final days</i></font>

36
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>we'd laugh together in blissful ignorance.</i></font>

37
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Word has it a strange hallucinogen 
has been circulating recently.</font>

38
00:04:05,490 --> 00:04:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A drug?!</font>

39
00:04:07,010 --> 00:04:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's chiefly popular 
among young aristocrats,</font>

40
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which makes me wonder 
how they're getting it.</font>

41
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only prominent nobles have the stuff.</font>

42
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what is this hallucinogen called?</font>

43
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jackal's Paradise.</font>

44
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At the time, it seemed a trivial matter.</i></font>

45
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But one day, some months later...</i></font>

46
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dylan's been jailed for treason?!</font>

47
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Given the circumstances,
 I doubt he can avoid the headsman.</font>

48
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's preposterous!</font>

49
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naturally, Dylan would never turn traitor.</font>

50
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:47,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone framed him.</font>

51
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And their goal is...</font>

52
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't mean... war?</font>

53
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Faris. They've secretly 
been pulling the strings.</font>

54
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The Holy Grail of Eris"?</font>

55
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dylan is a pillar of our border defense. 
They'll invade once he's dead.</font>

56
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then Dylan was sentenced 
to death so quickly because...</font>

57
00:05:11,710 --> 00:05:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We have rats in our midst.</font>

58
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could Daeg Gallus be using 
the drug to secure funds?</font>

59
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given its popularity 
with the upper nobility,</font>

60
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they almost certainly mean 
to erode our nation from within.</font>

61
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And amid it all, 
one man has seen a meteoric rise.</font>

62
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Simon Darkian!</font>

63
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Question him at once!</font>

64
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'd only plead ignorance.</font>

65
00:05:44,050 --> 00:05:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have no proof.</font>

66
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a disaster!</font>

67
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the poisoning accusation against 
Scarlett part of their plan as well?</font>

68
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that must be coincidence.</font>

69
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have no motive to harm Scarlett.</font>

70
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true... 
They want her on the throne.</font>

71
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That means without Scarlett, 
their plan falls apart.</i></font>

72
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In which case...</i></font>

73
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What am I thinking?!</i></font>

74
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sire, I suggest we make use of Scarlett.</font>

75
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their plan requires a pawn possessing 
the blood of the old imperial family.</font>

76
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Executing Scarlett will buy us a way out.</font>

77
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will stall them and sow the sentiment
that public executions are barbaric.</font>

78
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll task Kimberly Smith of the Violet 
Association with leading the outcry.</font>

79
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That will allow us 
to delay Dylan's execution.</font>

80
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait, wait.</font>

81
00:07:05,370 --> 00:07:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the meantime, I will gather 
proof of his innocence.</font>

82
00:07:08,650 --> 00:07:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Dolphy!</font>

83
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty!</font>

84
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commit the face of every person 
who pleads for Scarlett's life to memory.</font>

85
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their agents will be among them.</font>

86
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll show them all 
that we shall be the ones</font>

87
00:07:32,370 --> 00:07:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who will have the last laugh.</font>

88
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Supposing that I did engineer 
my daughter's execution,</font>

89
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what is that to you?</font>

90
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm doing this for her.</font>

91
00:07:52,490 --> 00:07:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Her"?</font>

92
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I have your permission to speak?</font>

93
00:07:58,370 --> 00:08:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

94
00:08:16,610 --> 00:08:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you feeling?</font>

95
00:08:19,490 --> 00:08:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I didn't know any better,
 I'd think you were worried about me.</font>

96
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I am. You're my wife.</font>

97
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, dear...</font>

98
00:08:33,180 --> 00:08:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't give me that nonsense.</font>

99
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A woman you don't sleep with and only 
see to exchange the occasional greeting</font>

100
00:08:42,300 --> 00:08:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">isn't what most people would call a wife.</font>

101
00:08:45,970 --> 00:08:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're thinking of a mere acquaintance.</font>

102
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you angry?</font>

103
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm only asking that you spare me 
your foolery, you dunderhead.</font>

104
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

105
00:09:00,410 --> 00:09:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you can hardly expect 
a young lady to spell it out.</font>

106
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may be a silly little girl,</font>

107
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet even I know the blood
 in my veins could spark a fire.</font>

108
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But do you expect me
 to just grin and bear it?</font>

109
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To just accept a life of 
being treated like a prisoner?</font>

110
00:09:23,610 --> 00:09:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that but a living death?</font>

111
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'd like to be very selfish 
and have some harsh words with you.</font>

112
00:09:35,990 --> 00:09:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

113
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe that when most people say 
"harsh words," they do mean <i>words</i>.</font>

114
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do forgive me.</font>

115
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back where I come from, 
we talk to dunderheads with our fists.</font>

116
00:09:58,650 --> 00:10:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a lawless place that must be.</font>

117
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've done a lot of thinking 
since I came to this country,</font>

118
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I've decided to live my life
as I please after all.</font>

119
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That <i>was</i> our dear Cornelia's dying wish.</font>

120
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was?</font>

121
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. And so...</font>

122
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you have a complaint, 
tell it to Cornelia Faris.</font>

123
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

124
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I actually went and did it!</i></font>

125
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do forgive me.</font>

126
00:10:37,060 --> 00:10:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my mother taught me to speak 
to dunderheads with my fists.</font>

127
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That was, um, a custom from
 the homeland of my friend's mother!</font>

128
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your friend...?</font>

129
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, something about the best way 
to deal with dunderheads.</font>

130
00:10:57,020 --> 00:11:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not that I mean to call 
Your Grace a dunderhead.</font>

131
00:11:03,890 --> 00:11:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's a little slap?</font>

132
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hurt a lot worse back then.</font>

133
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what else does your friend want?</font>

134
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I offer my head, perhaps?</font>

135
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-P-Perish the thought!</font>

136
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

137
00:11:23,470 --> 00:11:26,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you ever have need of it,
 you need only ask.</font>

138
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does Your Grace...</font>

139
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wish to die?</font>

140
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that must be it.</font>

141
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been longing for death, have I?</font>

142
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:51,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I deserve to be punished. Otherwise...</font>

143
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'd be too pitiful for words, robbed 
of her life through no fault of her own.</font>

144
00:12:01,550 --> 00:12:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connie.</font>

145
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may...</font>

146
00:12:12,620 --> 00:12:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have never once thought myself pitiful.</font>

147
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:24,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I felt anger and sadness as well.</font>

148
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I know how awkward 
and proud you are, Father.</font>

149
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't help yourself.</font>

150
00:12:31,130 --> 00:12:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you've no reason to pity me.</font>

151
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I know...</font>

152
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I came into this world loved.</font>

153
00:12:43,130 --> 00:12:48,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I know that you loved me, Father.</font>

154
00:13:00,290 --> 00:13:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's plenty I'd like to say to you, 
but as for the rest of my complaints,</font>

155
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I'll just have to 
tell them to Cornelia Faris.</font>

156
00:13:13,190 --> 00:13:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

157
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must know what that means.</font>

158
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I know. I know, all right.</i></font>

159
00:13:24,310 --> 00:13:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother was always saying it.</font>

160
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Scarlett...</i></font>

161
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have your casket made of jet.</i></font>

162
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a sacred wood, said to guide souls 
to the promised land.</i></font>

163
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I won't forget a blanket 
woven of moonworm cocoons.</i></font>

164
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't have you getting a chill.</i></font>

165
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Remember how often you caught colds 
when you were little?</i></font>

166
00:13:53,770 --> 00:13:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You grew feverish so quickly,
I couldn't take my eyes off you.</i></font>

167
00:13:58,100 --> 00:14:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know. Why don't I add 
lovely engravings to your casket?</i></font>

168
00:14:03,570 --> 00:14:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You never would settle 
for less than the best.</i></font>

169
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Really, you were always so willful and...</i></font>

170
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Had there been any other way,
I would've given anything for it!</i></font>

171
00:14:24,070 --> 00:14:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would have given my own life 
many times over!</i></font>

172
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only I'd told you even once 
that I loved you!</font>

173
00:14:53,590 --> 00:14:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, do your best for her.</font>

174
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Simon Darkian is with Daeg Gallus?</font>

175
00:15:03,410 --> 00:15:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia recently purchased 
the Saint Nicholas Hospital.</font>

176
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Campbell owned it, tax inspectors 
gave even blank books a pass.</font>

177
00:15:13,930 --> 00:15:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't mean Simon Darkian was 
in charge of those inspections, do you?</font>

178
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean just that.</font>

179
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A man named Edmond Park, 
who did the hospital's accounting,</font>

180
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was found murdered.</font>

181
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To silence him, most likely.</font>

182
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meaning they kept secret books.</font>

183
00:15:31,690 --> 00:15:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We may be able to round up 
the whole gang if we can locate them.</font>

184
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I entrust the matter to you.</font>

185
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

186
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On that note... 
I heard Simon Ulster passed.</font>

187
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My condolences. When is the funeral?</font>

188
00:15:49,470 --> 00:15:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today. Only for close family.</font>

189
00:15:52,850 --> 00:15:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be going alone?</font>

190
00:15:55,350 --> 00:15:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Why?</font>

191
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't say much has changed on our end.</font>

192
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Second Prince Roderick is still 
avoiding public appearances.</font>

193
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:08,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}SECOND PRINCE OF FARIS
RODERICK</font>

194
00:16:08,830 --> 00:16:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Third Princess Alexandra
 is still locked in the tower</font>

195
00:16:09,130 --> 00:16:13,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}THIRD PRINCESS OF FARIS
ALEXANDRA</font>

196
00:16:12,950 --> 00:16:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and on track to be burned.</font>

197
00:16:15,020 --> 00:16:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Fourth Prince Theophilis
 is already acting like he's king.</font>

198
00:16:19,010 --> 00:16:22,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}FOURTH PRINCE OF FARIS
THEOPHILIS</font>

199
00:16:20,210 --> 00:16:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear his followers have even
 picked a date for the coronation.</font>

200
00:16:24,690 --> 00:16:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then the one behind 
the Holy Grail of Eris must be...</font>

201
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed, Fourth Prince Theophilis 
seems the obvious suspect.</font>

202
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, Connie!</font>

203
00:16:35,050 --> 00:16:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mylene.</font>

204
00:16:36,370 --> 00:16:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are these ladies?</font>

205
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were just leaving.</font>

206
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mylene, how is your work?</font>

207
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm writing articles to sell to the papers
 on my way to becoming a real reporter.</font>

208
00:16:51,070 --> 00:16:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My latest is on the suspicious death 
of Edmond Park.</font>

209
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's Edmond Park?</font>

210
00:16:56,990 --> 00:17:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The head of an accounting firm. 
He was found murdered.</font>

211
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears to have been
a work-related vendetta.</font>

212
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His clients included the Raven Trading 
Company and Saint Nicholas Hospital.</font>

213
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did she say Saint Nicholas Hospital?</font>

214
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Mylene, isn't Saint Nicholas
 the hospital Earl Campbell used to run?</font>

215
00:17:18,290 --> 00:17:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you know all about it!</font>

216
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just between us, I hear Edmond Park 
and Earl Campbell were gambling buddies.</font>

217
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it seems one gambling den 
in particular was his favorite.</font>

218
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's under a restaurant called
 The Goat's Hoof.</font>

219
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you waiting for?</font>

220
00:17:42,850 --> 00:17:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did I get myself into this?</font>

221
00:17:45,050 --> 00:17:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing in a place like this?</font>

222
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dear me. It's Kimberly Smith 
of the Violet Association.</font>

223
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's not wearing pink?!</font>

224
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your order?</font>

225
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meat on the bone.</font>

226
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kind where top and bottom 
add up to seven.</font>

227
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So <i>that's</i> what you're here for.</font>

228
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, downstairs isn't open yet.</font>

229
00:18:12,860 --> 00:18:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what a shame.</font>

230
00:18:14,610 --> 00:18:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm only here to pick up
 something for Ed today.</font>

231
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

232
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assume you're here 
about the Edmond Park case.</font>

233
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who told you?</font>

234
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend. She wants to be a reporter.</font>

235
00:18:37,580 --> 00:18:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My. She has promise.</font>

236
00:18:40,090 --> 00:18:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you engaged to Randolph Ulster?</font>

237
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know who the Ulsters are?</font>

238
00:18:49,050 --> 00:18:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Ulster" isn't merely a surname.</font>

239
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's also a title for agents who 
dispose of the royal family's enemies.</font>

240
00:18:57,290 --> 00:18:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agents?</font>

241
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Randolph serves in the military now, 
but the late Simon Ulster trained him,</font>

242
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even though the duty 
has long since become a formality.</font>

243
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Excuse me, but why tell me this?</font>

244
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good question. I also—</font>

245
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

246
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it. Some kind of secret 
accounting ledger, I hear.</font>

247
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, thank you.</font>

248
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't those people...</font>

249
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They really must not want us 
reading that secret ledger.</font>

250
00:19:41,170 --> 00:19:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your eyes on me. 
Put it in your purse.</font>

251
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all the help I can give you.</font>

252
00:19:49,910 --> 00:19:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go out the back door. Hurry now.</font>

253
00:19:52,390 --> 00:19:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about you?</font>

254
00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need deadweight.</font>

255
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was trained by Simon Ulster as well.</font>

256
00:20:08,390 --> 00:20:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He should be at Simon's funeral now.</font>

257
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take good care of Junior.</font>

258
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what you should be doing.</font>

259
00:20:34,150 --> 00:20:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

260
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Grail?</font>

261
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw it was raining.</font>

262
00:21:03,870 --> 00:21:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you here?</font>

263
00:21:05,410 --> 00:21:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, the thing is, 
Kimberly left this in my care.</font>

264
00:21:14,860 --> 00:21:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times must I tell you
 not to act on your own?</font>

265
00:21:18,230 --> 00:21:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry.</font>

266
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Your Lordship was alone too.</font>

267
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So won't you call us even for today?</font>

268
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:31,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't I unnerve you?</font>

269
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon?</font>

270
00:21:33,650 --> 00:21:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My parents, my brother, 
Lily, my granduncle...</font>

271
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People close to me keep dying.</font>

272
00:21:41,610 --> 00:21:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think I really am
 like Death himself?</font>

273
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your fiancée...</font>

274
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">lost her last betrothed to another woman,
made a spectacle of herself at a ball,</font>

275
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">gets mixed up in one criminal 
incident after another,</font>

276
00:22:00,610 --> 00:22:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and, worst of all, she's haunted 
by the wickedest woman of the age.</font>

277
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't that unnerve <i>you</i>?</font>

278
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's leave together, Your Lordship.</font>

279
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

280
00:22:19,890 --> 00:22:21,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}THE HOLY GRAIL OF ERIS</font>

281
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:27,970
